file.name: query-params.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Structured query params
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  /v1/test:
    get:
      parameters:
        - schema:
            type: string
          in: query
          name: firstName
          required: true
        - schema:
            type: string
          in: query
          name: lastName
        - schema:
            type: number
          in: query
          name: age
        - schema:
            type: boolean
          in: query
          name: employed
          required: true
        - schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: string
              enum: ['ru', 'en', 'fr', 'de', 'jp']
          in: query
          name: languages
        - schema:
            type: array
            items:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Asset'
          in: query
          name: assets
        - schema:
            type: object
            additionalProperties: false
            properties:
              good:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: string
              bad:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: string
          in: query
          name: qualities
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
    parameters: []
components:
  schemas:
    Asset:
      title: Asset
      type: object
      properties:
        currency:
          type: string
        amount:
          type: integer
      required:
        - currency
        - amount
